Waxman Industries Inc is raising 25mln dlrs through an offering of convertible subordinateddebentures due 2007 with a 6-1/4 pct coupon and par pricing,said sole underwriter Drexel Burnham Lambert Inc.    The debentures are convertible into the company's commonstock at 14.375 dlrs per share, representing a premium of 25pct over the stock price when terms on the debt were set.    Moody's Investors Service Inc rates the debentures B-2.Proceeds will be used to repay short and long-termindebtedness. Reuter&#3;